<blockquote>
<p>You can suggest me some names if you want to, cause I'm already making their logos XD</p>
</blockquote>
<p>&quot;Descendants of the Two Dragons&quot; （双龙传人）<br />
&quot;Twin Dragons' Clan&quot; （双龙族）</p>
<p>I can sort of imagine the Chinese government keeping them as a secret ethnic minority group (since the extremely small faction mind as well be like a small clan of their own and it's not the first time an <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hui_people">ethnic group</a> is defined by religion).</p>
<p>When you mentioned serpent people, I imagined that sect members use Sarkic and CotBG rituals/surgeries to make their bodies more serpentine to resemble their divine parents. Also, they would look more cyborg and keep a roughly 50-50 balance between flesh and mechanical parts.</p>

